  "analysis": "MIPS cross-compiler is installed with libc available. The doomgeneric_img.c includes my_stdlib.h (custom stdlib). Other doom files include standard headers. The VM uses x86 syscall numbers (0=read, 1=write, 2=open, etc.) with MIPS SYSCALL instruction. We can't use standard MIPS libc since it uses MIPS syscall numbers (4000+). We need to create custom stdlib implementation with x86 syscall numbers.",
